                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 12
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "一日の授業が終わり、帰りのショートホームルームの時間。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 13
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "静子"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "SZ000031"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 19
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「毎日暑いですねぇ……みなさん、体調は大丈夫\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 20
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　ですか〜？」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 21
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 24
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "この教室で一番元気そうな岡野先生は、ダレ気味の\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 25
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "生徒たちを見て、心配そうにハの字眉を作っている。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 26
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "静子"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "SZ000032"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 32
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「みなさん若いんですから、しゃっきりしないとですよ、\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 33
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　しゃっきりと〜」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 34
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "クラスメイトＡ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "NP050002"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 37
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「エアコンが欲しいよ、静子ちゃんー」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 38
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "静子"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "SZ000033"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 44
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「ごめんなさい、今年は扇風機で我慢してくださいね〜」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 45
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 51
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "言いつつ、岡野先生は教室前方に置いてある扇風機を\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 52
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "『強』モードに上げた。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 53
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "静子"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "SZ000034"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 59
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「はぅぅん、困りました〜、夏休み前に疲れを\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 60
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　溜めすぎちゃうのは良くないですし……」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 61
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "静子"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "SZ000035"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 68
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「そうそう、夏バテには、ずばり糖分が効くんですよ〜」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 69
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "クラスメイトＢ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "NP060003"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 74
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「ええー、嘘だー！」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 75
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 78
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "ぽん、と手を打った岡野先生に、教室のそこここから\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 79
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "不平の声が漏れる。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 80
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "静子"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "SZ000036"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 88
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「本当ですよ〜、先生、嘘をついたりはしません〜〜」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 89
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "静子"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "SZ000037"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 95
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「かき氷でしょう、アイスクリームでしょう、水ようかん\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 96
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　にゼリーでしょう……夏においしいお菓子がいっぱい\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 97
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　あるのは、夏バテには糖分が効くからなんですよ〜」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 98
        }
    ]
}